.TH bank 1  "bank " 
.SH NAME
bank \- Manage gene\-banks: list / export / import
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbank\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage gene\-banks: list / export / import
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
bank\-list(1)
List every WAF / host that has proven techniques recorded
.TP
bank\-export(1)
Export the entire local gene\-bank corpus (proxy + per\-WAF) into a single JSON file
.TP
bank\-import(1)
Restore a previously\-exported envelope onto this machine
.TP
bank\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
